import React, { Component } from 'react'; import '../App.css'; import { Table } from 'reactstrap'; import TableHeader from './TableHeader'; class CycleA extends Component { render() { let weight = this.props.weight; let load = Math.max((this.props.weight-this.props.bar), 0); let toggle = {display: this.props.isToggle? 'block' : 'none'} function round(num) { return Math.round(num*2)/2; } return (
A 40% 5x {round(weight*4/10).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*4/10).toFixed(1)}
B 50% 5x {Math.round(weight*5/10).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*5/10).toFixed(1)}
C 60% 3x {Math.round(weight*6/10).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*6/10).toFixed(1)}
1 65% 5x {Math.round(weight*65/100).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*65/100).toFixed(1)}
2 75% 5x {Math.round(weight*75/100).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*75/100).toFixed(1)}
3 85% 5x+ {Math.round(weight*85/100).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*85/100).toFixed(1)}
) } } export default CycleA;
